public class WorldVertexIdentifier extends VertexIdentifier
A vertex identifier in a WorldGraph. Scopes a vertex identifier with a WorldCell. The cell for this identifier can be retrieved with worldCell() and the vertex (WorldVertex) with vertex().

jonathanl (shibo)
